On the 22/06/2026 I completed an atom exposure return template for them

1) Alto:
I got contribution from Attribution reports (monthly)
I got exposure from exposure report (monthly)
I got net return and Fund AUM from Due Dilligence table (no ramp up), same for the net return

For the count of long and short position I run Atom_count_position_alto.py
For Exposure, I run atom exposure_alto.py

2) Long Short:
I use the module atom_long_short_data.py
for exposure, I run atom_exposure_long_short
